      "content": "# operational-hub-profile model defines operational hub configurations\n\n`powerhouse/operational-hub-profile` (4 ops) defines operational hubs — teams or working groups that operate within a [[network-profile model represents network-level organizational entities]]. Bridges between network-level organization and individual [[builder-profile model describes individual contributor identities]].\n\n## Position in Ecosystem\n\nOrganization & Identity zone. Minimal operations suggest configuration-focused (name, description, membership rules).\n\n---\n\nTopics:\n- [[ecosystem map]]\n- [[object relations]]",
